This paper is related to the design and optimization of wireless local area networks (WLANs), specifically those using the channel bonding technique in IEEE 802.11ac. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves mathematical modeling and optimization, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper mentions simulations, which could indicate a connection to cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.PF (Performance).
